  "content": "<!-- Long-request popup -->\r\n<div id=\"long-request-overlay\" class=\"hidden\">\r\n  <div class=\"config-box\" style=\"width:380px;text-align:center\">\r\n    <div style=\"font-size:32px;margin-bottom:12px\">⏳</div>\r\n    <h3 style=\"margin:0 0 8px;font-size:16px;color:var(--text)\">Taking a while...</h3>\r\n    <p id=\"long-request-msg\" style=\"font-size:13px;color:var(--dim);margin:0 0 16px\">MA has been working for <span id=\"lr-elapsed\">30</span>s. You can cancel or let it keep going.</p>\r\n    <div class=\"btn-row\" style=\"justify-content:center;gap:10px\">\r\n      <button class=\"btn-cancel\" onclick=\"cancelLongRequest()\">Cancel</button>\r\n      <button class=\"btn-save\" onclick=\"dismissLongRequest()\">Let it finish</button>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <label style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;justify-content:center;margin-top:14px;font-size:12px;color:var(--dim);cursor:pointer\">\r\n      <input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"lr-autopilot-check\" style=\"accent-color:var(--accent)\" onchange=\"toggleAutoPilotFromPopup(this.checked)\"> Enable Auto Pilot (never show this again)\r\n    </label>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n  <div class=\"config-box\" style=\"width:520px\">\r\n    <div class=\"ingest-prog-header\">\r\n      <span id=\"ingest-prog-label\">Ingesting...</span>\r\n      <span id=\"ingest-prog-pct\" style=\"margin-left:auto;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums\"></span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"ingest-prog-bar\"><div class=\"ingest-prog-fill\" id=\"ingest-prog-fill\"></div></div>\r\n    <div id=\"ingest-prog-detail\" class=\"ingest-prog-detail\"></div>\r\n    <div id=\"ingest-prog-log\" class=\"ingest-prog-log\"></div>\r\n    <div id=\"ingest-prog-error\" class=\"ingest-prog-error hidden\"></div>\r\n    <div class=\"btn-row\" style=\"margin-top:12px;gap:8px\">\r\n      <button class=\"btn-cancel\" id=\"ingest-kill-btn\" onclick=\"killIngest()\">Stop</button>\r\n      <button class=\"btn-cancel hidden\" id=\"ingest-close-btn\" onclick=\"closeIngestProgress()\">Close</button>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>",
